-- News Corp. Offers to Acquire British Sky Broadcasting at 700 Pence a Share
-- Angela Cullen
-- 2010-06-15T06:36:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/news-corp-offers-to-buy-remaining-shares-of-bskyb-for-11-5-billion-cash.html

          
          
             News Corp. raised its offer for
British Sky Broadcasting Group Plc to 700 pence a share for the
shares it doesn’t own, valuing the company at 7.8 billion pounds
excluding News Corp.’s stake.  
          
          


  


        